{
  "stem": "14190.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember seeing a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So where was it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had to be some place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Life in ghetto, I don't know how long I was in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I think-- I think I was probably somewhere around eight or nine months there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe a little less.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I cannot even begin to tell you the-- the awful, awful time that we had there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First of all, I-- I right away got friendly with a group of kids that were older than I was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were very clever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They knew how to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they told me, Bachia, I'll show you how to get out of ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, so when you get out, what are you going to do then.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, we're going to go to marketplace.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We're going to get some food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We're going to get-- and we're going to get like those kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We'll be like those kids outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, very soon, very soon, since I was the smallest in the group, and the thinnest in the group, well, they dug out a hole beneath the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I could very easily, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And slowly, slowly, they did, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we-- in a group, sometimes three or four of us, would smuggle out of ghetto and would go to marketplace, and would get some-- you know, we were asking for-- for food, for-- for vegetables and stuff.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember distinctly-- oh, my.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I found-- I found a whole-- a whole package of food stamps, German food stamps for German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we figure out what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "First, I didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we figure out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And one of the boys that were in the group, he says, Barbara, see, you go to that store.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
